SetSlippageTolerance_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── when caller not comptroller
│  └── it should revert
└── when caller is comptroller
   ├── when tolerance exceeds max
   │  └── it should revert
   ├── when tolerance within limit
   │  ├── it should update the slippage tolerance
   │  └── it should emit a {SetSlippageTolerance} event
   ├── when tolerance at maximum
   │  ├── it should update the slippage tolerance
   │  └── it should emit a {SetSlippageTolerance} event
   └── when tolerance zero
      ├── it should update the slippage tolerance
      └── it should emit a {SetSlippageTolerance} event
